messages.message:
Circling back here, I'm game to move AIHub certifies to Wednesdays. The release coordinator docs were updated during the rewrite to indicate that certifying  the "newly-cut" aihub release branch doesn't happen until the week _after_ code-cut, so that's already handled (for instance, 25.12.0-aihub isn't being certified for the first time until tomorrow)

I won't make the schedule change this week as we've not announced it, and it will affect UAT completion pushes, but feel free to announce the new UAT cut-off broadly and loudly and we can change the cron schedule after tomorrow's builds. :+1:
